          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44094871/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44094871/" class="">第114页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/161476477/" class=" " title="蓝琉璃">蓝琉璃</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44094871">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">然而，呕吐感却是会让病人上医院求诊的第二大不适症，仅次于疼痛</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-18 18:51</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p> 然而，呕吐感却是会让病人上医院求诊的第二大不适症，仅次于疼痛</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

